Leinster Beats Defending Champ Toulouse 32-23 to Reach Heineken Cup Final

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-04-30T17:11:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-30/leinster-beats-defending-champ-toulouse-32-23-to-reach-heineken-cup-final.html
Leinster beat defending champion
Toulouse 32-23 to advance to the final of rugby’s Heineken Cup.  Jamie Heaslip and Brian O’Driscoll scored tries and
Jonathan Sexton kicked 22 points in Dublin as Leinster avenged a
loss to Toulouse in last year’s semifinals. Leinster will face
the winner of tomorrow’s game between  Northampton Saints  and
Perpignan in the May 21 final at Cardiff.  Florian Fritz and Louis Picamoles scored tries for
Toulouse, while David Skrela kicked 10 points.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  